text: Sarpang District is one of the 20 districts in Bhutan. The administrative centre is Sarpang. There are 12 village blocks: *Chhuzagang Gewog *Chhudzom Gewog *Dekiling Gewog *Gakiling Gewog *Gelephu Gewog *Jigmechhoeling Gewog *Samtenling Gewog *Senghe Gewog *Serzhong Gewog *Shompangkha Gewog *Tareythang Gewog *Umling Gewog Category:Districts of Bhutan
title: Sarpang District
